FBIS3-58470 "drweu010_i_94004" FBIS-WEU-94-010 Document Type:Daily Report 14 Jan 1994 FRANCE Leotard Says Military Sales to Taiwan Assured LD1301143494 Paris France-Inter Radio Network in French 1400 GMT 13 Jan 94 LD1301143494 Paris France-Inter Radio Network Language: French Article Type:BFN [Text] [Defense Minister] Francois Leotard says France will continue to sell motorized armored vehicles and nonoffensive secondary military materiel to Taiwan. Taiwan has said it has no doubt that France will respect the contracts for deliveries that have already been signed, but it is worried about future deliveries of spare parts. Jean-Marie Le Pen says France has acted dishonorably by abandoning Taiwan to normalize its relations with China.
